devdoc.details: Inherits ownership & employee access control from `employe_assignment`

params.employee: The address of the newly assigned employee
params.role: The role assigned to the employee

params.employee: The address of the removed employee

params.newOwner: The address of the new owner
params.oldOwner: The address of the previous owner

assignNewEmployee(address,string).details: Only the owner can assign new employees. Validates role and address.

params.newEmployee: Address of the employee to be assigned
params.role: Role to assign to the employee

changeOwner(address).details: Only the current owner can call this function. Validates the new owner address.

returns._0: bool True if the account has the specified role

removeEmployee(address,string).details: Only the owner can remove employee roles. Validates role and current assignment.

params.employee: Address of the employee to remove the role from
params.role: Role to remove from the employee

returns.balances: Current balance expressed in whole ETH

transfer_to_loan_contract(uint256).details: Only callable by employees. Validates amount > 0 and sufficient balance before sending.
